      • put

        public void put​(dev.kkorolyov.simpleprops.Properties imageConfig)
        Parses images from a configuration file. Each entry is an image name mapped to an arbitrary-length array of base images. Each base image is first parsed as the name of an image found in this pool, or a filename of an image on the file system if no such image exists in this pool.
        Parameters:
        imageConfig - image configuration file
